  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"maincontent\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eNothing beats the magic of a winter holiday in the mountains. Whether you’re skiing or snowboarding in the Alps, husky-sledding through frozen forests in Scandinavia, snowshoeing in Poland’s Tatra mountains, or simply soaking up the snowy splendour from the hot tub of a mountain hideaway in the Dolomites, we’d love to hear about your favourite winter getaways in Europe.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you have a relevant photo, do send it in –\u003cstrong\u003e but it’s your words that will be judged\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003efor the competition\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKeep your tip to about 100 words\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe best tip of the week, chosen by \u003ca href=\"https://www.lonelyplanet.com/\" data-link-name=\"in body link\"\u003eTom Hall of Lonely Planet\u003c/a\u003e, will \u003cstrong\u003ewin a £200 voucher to stay at a \u003ca href=\"https://www.coolstays.com/\" data-link-name=\"in body link\"\u003eCoolstays\u003c/a\u003e property\u003c/strong\u003e – the company has more than 3,000 worldwide. The best tips will appear in the Guardian Travel section and website.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe’re sorry, but for legal reasons \u003cstrong\u003eyou must be a UK resident \u003c/strong\u003eto enter this competition.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"de55ec9f-e142-4ac9-b99a-1b163098f93b\" data-spacefinder-role=\"inline\" data-spacefinder-type=\"model.dotcomrendering.pageElements.ImageBlockElement\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"img-2\"\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/3c3637f953928bdb44fc02ed05648f6f8fc83a47/0_0_6100_520/master/6100.jpg?width=620\u0026amp;dpr=2\u0026amp;s=none\" media=\"(min-width: 660px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 660px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk